Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chroniclers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean those folks who are always tirelessly writing the town journal? {年代記作家か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it "history" rather than "journals".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:25.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all they do for a living is sit down and get money from the nobility and church to write words all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:29.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chroniclers also collect various folktales.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to go up north, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what the road is like on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A business opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:40.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish it were.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing this for my own interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though as a merchant I know it's not profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you've found yourself quite a fun hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you want someone from the Rowen guild, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple when you're a merchant of my caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my deepest gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guy Bartose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an old timer who deals in metals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A fearless guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He works with folk that you'd be best staying away from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I already ate on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got them while I was buying the bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark had that kid deliver them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll definitely laugh if you read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:47.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, there's way too many characters to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:55.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, there's too many complicated combinations of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you at least tried to learn at some point?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but I got annoyed and quit. {じゃが腹が立って止めた}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can catch prey without being able to read. {字が読めなくても獲物がとれるからの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:02.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:09.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"This year's Northern Military expedition has been canceled, so be cautious when buying battle equipment."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they had told us before we lost out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Without information, us merchants are like blindfolded soldiers on a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,there's somewhere I'd like to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're just joking, could you stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are weak against this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I go alone then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I say no, you'd go anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:05:01.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That coin isn't worth as much as a Trenni silver, so you won't annoy anyone if you use it on small items.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go have a good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe going alone wouldn't be fun after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take me with you, you can have the coin back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of business is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to meet a fellow guild member...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:26.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it'd be bad for us to be seen together, I could stay farther away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you be able to take me along then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:37.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have to go somewhere else after meeting this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:41.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you came along, you'd have to wait outside the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow I'll keep you company the whole day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so bear with it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't want to get in the way of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll mope around alone. {dictionary doesn't know "to mope around", change it pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:01.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:07.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are two people in the room when you get back, could you go out again for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:13.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind spending the whole day in here after getting to see such a cute face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:14.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, right now I like it best being by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here yet. He should be soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the guy the size of an upright coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An upright coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for getting us that room. {@ ulrezaj, change it to "getting us in the inn"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you ordered quite a bit of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My fussy companion was singing its praises.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you have a good eye for fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy more like those again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said the carp was especially good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:55.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The carp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business with Bartose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe I'd show you around the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... If we had a chance to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect we could share some information...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:21.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo's been nagging me to take her around the town since this morning. {original: Horo was nagging to look around the town since this morning.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, I could at least show Horo around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:32.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is I don't have any work to do today, so I have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, if I stayed here alone I'd just drink away my earnings anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she might have already left the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, if she's in I'll try inviting her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to discuss the inventory restocking there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, come along too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you must be Craft Lawrence-san{added -san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Guy Bartose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're interested in legends from the north?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a lead on some kind of business opportunity{<- added "opportunity"}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for my own interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good tastes for your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:34.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only became interested in legends and folktales recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:38.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've traveled between various regions for some decades now as a merchant,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:41.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought I knew everything about those few regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day it came to me –
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People have been traveling here for many hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:53.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I know absolutely nothing about that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:59.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't travel into the distant past, and I no longer have the energy to travel to faraway lands at my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:02.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I started wanting to learn more about the past, even if just through stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's a way to find out more about a past I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one from that period is alive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the memories we call "legends" continue to live on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and teach us things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:27.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The townsfolk don't think highly of the people inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Outsiders who are being chased by the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:33.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the sort that'd be hung if they went to Rubinhaigen. {(check place name)}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... sulfur?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:50.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be a good merchant if you're familiar with medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:55.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, you could say this wall's primary purpose is to block out this air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There seem to be a lot of birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:06.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the poisonous fumes in the air don't always smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:10.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what the church would call "the hand of the reaper"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It does feel as though his hand might reach out to you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:19.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many alchemists are living in this district?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:24.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Including the apprentices, maybe 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:28.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Accidents happen a lot, so it's hard to say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a lot of profit in dealing with{dealing in?} alchemists?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thinks of alchemy as magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality, their work has always just consisted of things like heating up metal, or using corrosive acids to melt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:46.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's also true that there are those who really study magic here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the rumors I've heard, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The inhabitants of this district are good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we are trading,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I won't be caught calling them bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The person we're meeting is quite easygoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My, a handsome boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I get the feeling he thinks I'm a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:50.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, shall I introduce you as one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is dark enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:57.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, could a witch be as beautiful as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:01.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They say many women have been called witches because of their beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're full of flattery, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've made a few beds here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway big sis, today this gentleman here... {overruled.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Craft Lawrence, a traveling merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Might Dean Rubens be available?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you didn't tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Dean Rubens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A very manly name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Deanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what business might you have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:40.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, let me apologize for barging in on you so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Rubens, I've heard that—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Deanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:46.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:52.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I've heard that you are well-versed in legends of the north, Deanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:53.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The north?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:54.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this was going to be business talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:03.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully I'll know the story you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'd like to learn about is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...the legend of a village called Yoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The village that was destroyed by the moon-hunting bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:16.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... If I'm not mistaken it was around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:24.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon-hunting bear, pronounced "Irawa Wir Muheidehende".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the town that was destroyed by that bear, Yoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:33.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're quite old stories, but there are a few about that bear in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:39.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it say anything about Yoitsu's location?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoitsu's location?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For certain reasons, I'm looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Location... Location...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:48.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Location...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:05.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of a town called Renose, situated at the base of the river Roam a ways north of Proania?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They deal in pelts and lumber, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is an ancient tale told there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:15.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"A long time ago, a giant wolf appeared in the village."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"She called herself Horou of Yoitsu,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"and was so big you had to look up to see her."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"She was thought to be punishment from heaven,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"but she said she had come from deep within the forests of{orig "to the east"}{changed, since "within the forests to the east" can have two different meanings} the east,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"and was on a journey towards the south."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:36.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"She loved to drink, and at times would take the form of a young maiden and dance with the girls in the village."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:41.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"She looked beautiful and young, but possessed a wolf's tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:44.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"The village has had abundant harvests for many years since then."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"We called her 'Horou of the wheaten tail'." {"We"? She was there in that town?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that helpful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:56.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The area between Renose and the deep forests of{orig: "to"} the east is limited. {well duh, every area is limited}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a solid clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely repay you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:08.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can tell, even being chased by the Church, I love ancient legends from pagan lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:15.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, only the ones in their original form, rather than the ones that have been altered due to influence from the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a traveling merchant,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure you've heard some interesting stories, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd allow me to hear some, that would be more than enough thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let me tell you the story of a wheat farming region in the south,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:34.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and its abundant harvest that was governed by a certain wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:41.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really been a while since I got excited over legends of dragons and magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:45.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling I was always thinking of those sorts of tales when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it makes me wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I stop being able to believe in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Upstream of the Roam river there's a town called Renose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:13.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd gotten some information about Niohira already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation's changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So the rumors that you fell out with your companion were true then.  {<-- 連れと仲違いという噂本当だったか}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't hide it, Mr. Popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:35.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's well known you've got a beautiful nun in a good hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you don't even fear God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:40.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My companion and I aren't in that kind of relationship. {norgus: http://eow.alc.co.jp/%E9%85%92%E3%81%AE%E3%81%95%E3%81%8B%E3%81%AA/UTF-8/?ref=wl}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you mean by a fall out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:50.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard just earlier that your companion was wandering around with a young man from the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they were having quite a bit of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:56.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Amati-san... huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Already given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had business and couldn't be with her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And since Amati...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:10.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...had free time on his hands, he agreed to show her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:17.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it turned out to be boring, but that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:24.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, if I heard my Adelle was walking around with Amati,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to stand still!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I'd play around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:30.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:35.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know how formidable he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:44.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away from home to start trading and became quite successful on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any woman would fall for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd burn up in flames of envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:58.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'd bake Amati-san a tasty pie on those flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Adelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:06.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll warn you as a former fellow traveling merchant – watch out for that Amati.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:11.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When guys that age get carried away... they'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:24.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The village that was destroyed by the moon-hunting bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Amati?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:37.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably parted ways downstairs. {<-- verify}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Probably" you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he buy that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,help me out a bit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:04.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:11.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he buy anything else for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is high quality fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it still loses to my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:31.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Accepting such a gift from him means I'll need to somehow repay him. {<-- verify}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:35.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was going to be a free night out for you, but look at the debt I'm facing now. {"going to be a free night out for you"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were scheming something after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:44.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be using the money I was planning to give to you for the festival as repayment for the scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he ask about our relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:51.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be bad if people got suspicious of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:20:03.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him I'm a traveling nun whom you rescued just as some bad people were about to sell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:10.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I took on a large debt to you, my rescuer, and because I have no way of paying you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:15.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been praying for your safe journey in order to repay it, being the ill-fated woman I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sob sob sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to put up such an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:22.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After he heard this, he suddenly bought me this scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a die that shows you your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:32.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was crafted into a beautiful shape wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely sell for a good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you'd be able to sell something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a naturally formed rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not man-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any particular use for it, and it's often sold as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:50.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell I'm not lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:50.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks a lot like gold, so it can be used to trick people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't see anyone else buying these, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there were a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:04.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fortune teller who was using these to see the future was very accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I was surprised at her skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She also told us lots of other reasons to promote their sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how it can heal sicknesses, or drive away demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,or awaken love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying all that when everyone's in high spirits during a festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amati won the bid for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He bid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I'd seen an auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was in a frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrite, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:43.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I worked through Bartose-san's connections, I wonder if this could be profitable?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to bother you so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My master asked me to pass on a messa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:59.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:09.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:10.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:12.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:51.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wolf and Unbridged Divide
